cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.MM 

This paper deals with gait recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a statistical approach for feature extraction, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation framework and database made publicly available can be useful for human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
